Title: To the Waterworks
Description:
Getting the Waterworks up and running is our first objective. Nothing else we do matters if we can't get power to the facility.

Meet up with Dagran and ZZ-01-47 once you get there. And try to keep them on the sidelines. I don't want to explain to Moira that her son was injured, or worse, under my care.
ObjectivesText: Meet up with Dagran and ZZ-01-47 at the Waterworks.
RewardText: This place is a mess! I think Zee-Zee and I will stay up here where it's dry.
